"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=utf-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:169
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"You've entered Zoltan territory. This species is not renowned for giving "
"anything for nothing, but you can always be assured a fair hearing."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:170
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"The Zoltan patrol their borders but let you pass when you ID as Federation. "
"Let's hope they won't be so courteous to the Rebels."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:171
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"You arrive in Zoltan space. From what you have heard they anticipated the "
"coming war and made preparations to hold their borders."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:172
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"You're far from Federation home space here in Zoltan territory, and it's not"
" clear whether the authorities will have any goodwill remaining. Still, you "
"have to push forward."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:173
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[5]"
msgstr ""
"You've arrived in a Zoltan sector. These energy filled humanoids are "
"sometimes too fair, but don't even think that won't apply to you. Here, you "
"have the same rights as other races, despite belonging to the Federation."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:174
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[6]"
msgstr ""
"You've arrived in a Zoltan sector. You can be assured you'll find high-tech "
"weaponry in their stores. And maybe you'll be destroyed by this very "
"weaponry..."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:175
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[7]"
msgstr ""
"The inscription on the beacon at the entrance to this Zoltan sector reads: "
"\"Long live the Zoltan court, the most humane court in the Galaxy!\""

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:176
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[8]"
msgstr ""
"Judging by the border guards who met you at this sector's entrance, the "
"Zoltans don't intend to give up just like that, even if there are too few of"
" them to detain the Rebels for long."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:177
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[9]"
msgstr ""
"The Zoltan sector is always distinguished by exemplary order and strict "
"enforcement of laws. But with the advent of the Rebels, much will change "
"here..."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:178
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[10]"
msgstr ""
"Remember, the main thing for Zoltans is the law and the way it is observed. "
"If you follow their rules, perhaps you'll fly through the sector without any"
" additional \"adventures\"."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:179
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[11]"
msgstr ""
"Whether you will be met peacefully by the Zoltan or you will be shot at — it"
" depends only on you. But be aware that because of the war, the borders of "
"their sector are vigilanty guarded..."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:180
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTAN\"]/text[12]"
msgstr ""
"The Zoltans are one of the most ancient races in the Galaxy. Billions of "
"years ago, they transcended their physical bodies and took on the form of "
"pure energy. Although they pride themselves as being an \"absolutely just\" "
"society, they tend to come across as immoral and condescending towards other"
" races."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:188
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"STORE_ZOLTAN\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"The Zoltan are fascinated by other species, and have set up something of an "
"alien knick-knack shop here. Why not take a look?"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:189
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"STORE_ZOLTAN\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"A human ship hails: \"My friends! Please, there is nothing I don't have, and"
" there is nothing worth wanting that I can't get. Why not make yourself at "
"home and take a look around my shop?\""

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:190
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"STORE_ZOLTAN\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"A Mantis crew here has hunkered down in the abdomen of a long-dead space-"
"whale - the only way, presumably, for them to operate their black-market "
"trade without detection. Worth a look?"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:202
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ZOLTAN\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"There are some mineral-rich asteroids here that the Zoltan have left idle, "
"but you've none of the necessary equipment to mine them."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:203
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ZOLTAN\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"You have to admit - Zoltan space is a beautiful and peaceful place indeed. "
"However, re-engaging the FTL and finishing your mission is your priority, "
"not sight-seeing."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:204
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ZOLTAN\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"A light asteroid field is entering the atmosphere of a nearby planet - a "
"fireworks show on a galactic scale. There's little for it but to take in the"
" ambience and program the next jump."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:206
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ZOLTAN\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"You stumble upon some Zoltan military vessels engaging in combat training. "
"Their Energy Shields are impressive, but you note how quickly beam and ion "
"weaponry take them down."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:207
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ZOLTAN\"]/text[5]"
msgstr ""
"You don't have time to hail the Zoltan ship that was waiting at this beacon "
"before it jumps away. They are a careful race."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:208
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ZOLTAN\"]/text[6]"
msgstr ""
"A Zoltan shipyard is stationed at this beacon. You admire the display of "
"hundreds of glowing Zoltan performing delicate exterior work on a massive "
"transport ship."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:209
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ZOLTAN\"]/text[7]"
msgstr ""
"A message broadcast from a nearby planet announces the presence of an "
"ancient Zoltan monastery available for visiting. Likely just a tourist trap,"
" but still too bad you don't have the time to visit."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:222
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_DISTRESS_MANTIS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your jump interrupts a Zoltan security ship as it follows a Mantis pirate "
"into an asteroid field. They message you, \"Your presence here will continue"
" to be tolerated - but please, do not interfere.\""

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:227
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_DISTRESS_MANTIS\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Interfere and save the Mantis ship."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:229
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_DISTRESS_MANTIS\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Sometimes you have to bet on the underdog - even on the rare occasions that "
"the underdog is a Mantis warship. You set off for the heart of the asteroid "
"field and engage the Zoltan there."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:235
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_DISTRESS_MANTIS\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Interfere and help the Zoltan ship."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:237
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_DISTRESS_MANTIS\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You overtake the Zoltan and catch up with the Mantis ship in the asteroid "
"belt. Time to make some friends."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:243
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_DISTRESS_MANTIS\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Don't intervene."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:245
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_DISTRESS_MANTIS\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Zoltan know their business better than most — best to leave them to it. "
"You prepare to jump."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:252
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_DISTRESS_SHELL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You arrive to find a lumbering Zoltan freighter with no one at the helm. "
"It's a mystery what happened to the crew, but it'd be a shame to let the "
"opportunity go to waste."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:268
#, fuzzy
msgid "data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You come to a Zoltan trade and supply hub — everything the weary traveler "
"needs, provided they have the right documentation."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:270
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Try to talk your way in."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:274
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB\"]/choice[@req=\"teleporter\"]/text"
msgstr "(Teleporter) Beam directly to the civilian deck."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:276
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB\"]/choice[@req=\"teleporter\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You re-materialize in a dark corner of the main concourse and are able to "
"conduct your investigations in peace."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:284
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB\"]/choice[@req=\"CREW_ENERGY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Zoltan Crewmember) Present their official documentation and pay the entry "
"fee."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:286
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB\"]/choice[@req=\"CREW_ENERGY\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"They scan ID that declares your crewmember an official citizen, collect "
"their fee, and let you pass."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:297
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB\"]/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "Leave this place."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:299
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB\"]/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You don't have the papers - well, the neuro-laced identity bracelets - to "
"get in, so best not to try."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:307
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB_TALK\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"They don't see many of your species in these parts, and you stick out like a"
" Casvagarian Sea Slug in a Plutonian Shrimp Stew. You make it back to the "
"ship with a gang of Zoltan guards in tow!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:312
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB_TALK\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"You pose as traders and succeed in bypassing airlock security — however, "
"it's only a matter of time before someone realizes your ID cards are "
"counterfeit!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:321
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB_SUCCESS\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"You head into a ship supply store. It is a well-equipped, self-service "
"affair. An order is dialled into a terminal, scrap is deposited, and the "
"item is dispatched from a nearby chute."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:328
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB_SUCCESS\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"You head into the cantina for gossip. Topics of conversation in the cantina "
"range from crop distribution microbes to the joys of Slug pleasure cruises."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:332
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TRADE_HUB_SUCCESS\"]/event[2]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You overhear one group discussing a newly discovered planet yet to have "
"first contact, and note down its location."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:341
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_QUEST_PRIMITIVES\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You arrive at the primitive planet that you heard about at the cantina and "
"are surprised to see a Zoltan ship facing off against a Rebel assault craft."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:345
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_QUEST_PRIMITIVES\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You tap into their frequency and hear the Rebel captain yelling, \"We are "
"liberating this planet in the name of the new Galactic government! These "
"aliens will not be left in ignorance where they cannot be of use!\""

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:347
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_QUEST_PRIMITIVES\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Interfere — make first contact with the primitive aliens."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:349
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_QUEST_PRIMITIVES\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The local people - furry, one-eyed tree lizard things - begin chanting when "
"they see you. Suddenly the sky is lit by laser fire — the Zoltan opened fire"
" on your ship! You dash back to the shuttle and join the fight."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:354
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_QUEST_PRIMITIVES\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Protect the aliens' way of life — Attack the Rebel ship."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:356
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_QUEST_PRIMITIVES\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"These creatures should be left to develop at their own pace. You direct all "
"weapons on the Rebel ship and begin the firing sequence."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:361
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_QUEST_PRIMITIVES\"]/choice/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Leave this place."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:363
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_QUEST_PRIMITIVES\"]/choice/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You don't want to alert the Rebels of your presence and you don't want to "
"anger the Zoltan in their territory. The best solution is to leave."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:380
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FREE_AUGMENT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"A Zoltan academy sits docked just outside the beacon perimeter. They're "
"happy to show you the fruits of their labor, and offer something to take "
"home with you."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:385
#, fuzzy
msgid "data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FREE_MAP\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Zoltan stationed near this beacon are happy to receive you. As they give"
" you the formal tour of their ship you spy some local star charts and "
"mentally log the details."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:391
#, fuzzy
msgid "data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON\"]/text"
msgstr "Something strikes you as odd about a moon in the distance."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:393
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Check it out."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:397
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Leave it be."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:399
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You try not to fixate on the moon in the aft scanner as you set the "
"coordinates for the next jump."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:403
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON\"]/choice[@req=\"DRONES_BOARDER\"]/text"
msgstr "(Boarding Drone) Send a drone to probe the surface."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:405
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON\"]/choice[@req=\"DRONES_BOARDER\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Initial scans indicate a network of caves not far underground. You launch a "
"boarding drone and it breaks through the surface into the cavern below."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:412
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON\"]/choice[@req=\"DRONES_BOARDER\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your drone discovers a vast cave network and evidence of excavation. Buried "
"deep below you find a Zoltan scientist, still hard at work. He tells you "
"that all his colleagues are long dead. You decide not to ask questions and "
"offer to let him join your crew."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:422
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_CHECK\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"A closer inspection reveals signs of habitation on the surface, but nothing "
"else particularly interesting."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:425
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_CHECK\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"Sending a shuttle to explore a beckoning cave system you discover signs of a"
" battle — and a still-functioning weapon!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:429
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_CHECK\"]/event[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"A deep scan of the surface reveals a cave system that runs for miles, and "
"what looks like a scrap heap left over from some heavy-duty construction."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:433
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_CHECK\"]/event[4]/text"
msgstr ""
"It looks as if a team could break through the fragile layer of the moon's "
"surface into a hidden cavern."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:435
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_CHECK\"]/event[4]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attempt to detonate some explosives to break through the surface."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:437
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_CHECK\"]/event[4]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "You plant the explosives and detonate them from a safe distance away."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:448
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_CHECK\"]/event[4]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"Explosives are too valuable to waste on excavation work. Let's get out of "
"here."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:456
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_EXPLOSION\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"A portion of the surface layer is destroyed in an impressive display, "
"revealing miles of caves. You don't have time to fully explore them, but you"
" find some remains of an old subterranean base that could be useful."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:460
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_EXPLOSION\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"The explosives are set remotely, but the detonation achieves nothing. What a"
" waste."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:463
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_EXPLOSION\"]/event[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your explosives reveal the 'cave' is actually a secret base, located in a "
"network of bunkers just under the surface. Everyone inside is dead; some "
"Mantis clearly came through here recently. It looks like the Zoltan were "
"researching advanced ship weaponry. You take one of their better examples "
"back to your ship."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:478
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FIGHT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"A Zoltan ship makes contact. \"The nature of the day is rotational. The "
"fever is emaciated. The reason is-\" They've caught some nasty deep space "
"dementia. Before you can consider finding help for them, they open fire."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:479
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FIGHT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"You're surprised when a stationary Zoltan ship opens fire. It appears there "
"are aggressive pugilists even among the 'enlightened'."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:480
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FIGHT\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"You receive a message, \"This area is off limits. Submit your ship to "
"processing.\" It's only one guard ship in a lonely beacon. You decide to "
"fight your way out."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:481
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FIGHT\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"You discover a number of Zoltan civilian ships fighting off pirates. "
"Unfortunately one ship mistakes your purpose and moves in to attack! They "
"are refusing all communication; you have no choice but to fight."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:482
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FIGHT\"]/text[5]"
msgstr ""
"Like many areas in Zoltan space, the residents of this sector prepared well "
"for Galactic war. The military here seem to have given up reasoning with "
"foreigners, preferring instead to attack on sight!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:483
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FIGHT\"]/text[6]"
msgstr ""
"A Zoltan ship is waiting at this beacon. They request your identification, "
"but radiation from the sun in this system is disrupting your communications."
" They take your silence for aggression and move in to attack."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:484
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FIGHT\"]/text[7]"
msgstr ""
"The Zoltan ship patrolling this area hails you: \"This area is off limits. "
"Secrecy is vital.\" They power their weapons."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:494
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PIRATE\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"\"Emergency, all ships in range, we are under attack!\" The frequency "
"matches a nearby Zoltan ship; you move in on their pursuer. They take your "
"intervention as a cue to jump away. Cowards."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:495
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PIRATE\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"You jump just in time to witness a Zoltan ship's FTL drive overload. In "
"their final moments they implore you not to get involved, but it's too late "
"- their attacker is already upon you!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:496
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PIRATE\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"Despite their precautions, pirates have begun to harass the local Zoltan "
"settlements across this sector. One such pirate spots your ship and moves in"
" to attack."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:497
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PIRATE\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"A ship with pirate markings demand that you surrender. These are sad times "
"when even Zoltan space is beset by pirates. You doubt these fools will be "
"missed."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:498
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PIRATE\"]/text[5]"
msgstr ""
"You spot a pirate ship looting a small Zoltan cruiser. They spot you and "
"move in to attack before your FTL drive has a chance to recharge."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:501
#, fuzzy
