#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:509
#, fuzzy
msgid "data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_MANTIS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You pick up the last broadcast from a rupturing Zoltan freighter: \"The "
"Mantis, they're here, please-\" You're interrupted by fire off the port bow!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:514
#, fuzzy
msgid "data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ENGI\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You jump into a debris field that used to be a Zoltan cruiser. "
"Unfortunately, its Engi escort takes you for the attacker and retaliates! "
"They refuse all hails."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:520
#, fuzzy
msgid "data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ASTEROID\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You arrive in an asteroid field and are greeted by a Zoltan guard, \"By "
"attempting to access these closed mining fields, you are in violation of the"
" Natural Mineral Protection Act. Your weaponry will be confiscated for "
"processing.\" You don't have time for this."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:533
#, fuzzy
msgid "data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_LIFERAFT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You pick up a Zoltan life raft floating in space. Its inhabitant asks you to"
" retake his ship from the pirates who recently commandeered it. \"I'm "
"certain it is clear,\" he concludes, \"that it is necessary to neutralize "
"them without smashing my vessel to smithereens.\""

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:537
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_LIFERAFT\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Engage the pirates."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:544
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_LIFERAFT\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Leave this place."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:546
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_LIFERAFT\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You refuse to get his ship back, but still offer to drop him off at the next"
" station. The Zoltan is displeased, but directs you to a nearby starbase "
"just the same."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:552
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_LIFERAFT_HIRE\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"He responds haughtily, \"You would presume I would work under your command "
"after such a display of... prowess? No, I must decline.\""

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:555
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_LIFERAFT_HIRE\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"He responds defeatedly, \"I suppose I have nowhere else to go without a "
"ship. I accept your offer.\""

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:565
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_SCIENCE_DOCK\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"What appears to be a Zoltan research ship requests permission to dock."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:567
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_SCIENCE_DOCK\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Dock with them."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:571
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_SCIENCE_DOCK\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Have them keep their distance."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:573
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_SCIENCE_DOCK\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "They leave without a word."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:579
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_SCIENCE_DOCK_LIST\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr "You allow them to approach... it was reckless of you: they open fire!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:583
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_SCIENCE_DOCK_LIST\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"We have been studying the relationships between the species and have "
"determined that the 'Federation' still has potential to be a net positive "
"for the galaxy. Please accept this gift to aid your journey.\""

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:590
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_RIFT_FIGHT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You come to a quiet part of Zoltan space and unexpectedly stumble upon an "
"ancient Zoltan wise man who has managed to harness the power of a spatial "
"rift, but seems to have been driven completely mad by the power. \"Choose "
"your doom,\" he demands. And why are you not surprised?"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:592
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_RIFT_FIGHT\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Mantis."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:594
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_RIFT_FIGHT\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"You like a challenge. So be it!\" Nearby, a wormhole forms and a confused,"
" angry Mantis ship hurtles toward you!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:599
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_RIFT_FIGHT\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Slug."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:601
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_RIFT_FIGHT\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Do not be fooled, Federation, by a soft underbelly.\" You detect a "
"wormhole opening up, and seconds later a Slug ship is attacking from the "
"other direction!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:606
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_RIFT_FIGHT\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Rock."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:608
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_RIFT_FIGHT\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"A hardened foe for a hardened veteran.\" You detect a wormhole opening up,"
" and a Rock ship appears with guns blazing. It appears they were in combat "
"when they were thrust across space-time."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:613
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_RIFT_FIGHT\"]/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "Crystal."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:615
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_RIFT_FIGHT\"]/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The old Zoltan is quiet for a moment, and then whispers, \"Are you sure? "
"Well, so be it then.\" A huge wormhole opens, and from within it looms a "
"Crystalline ship, prepared for war."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:662
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_RIFT_SUCCESS_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"When he sees you have emerged victorious, the Zoltan wise man enters a rage."
" Rifts threaten to tear space apart until, instead, the Zoltan implodes, "
"sending a blast wave of scrap and salvage dragged here from distant worlds "
"in your direction."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:665
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_RIFT_SUCCESS_2\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"When he sees you have emerged victorious, the Zoltan wise man enters a rage."
" A bright flash pierces the space nearby, and you suddenly find yourself "
"near an empty beacon... As another surprise, you find a new crew member on "
"board!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:669
#, fuzzy
msgid "data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_CREW_SCAN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You arrive at a Zoltan security checkpoint set up in a perimeter around the "
"beacon. \"Travelling vessel, you will submit to crew profiling to identify "
"fugitives of the empire.\""

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:671
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_CREW_SCAN\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "You don't have time for such nonsense. Attack!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:673
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_CREW_SCAN\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Expecting resistance, their Energy Shield is raised and ready for combat."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:678
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_CREW_SCAN\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Submit to profiling."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:682
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_CREW_SCAN\"]/choice[@req=\"slug_crew\"]/text"
msgstr "(Slug Crewmember) Have your Slug talk them into letting you go."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:684
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_CREW_SCAN\"]/choice[@req=\"slug_crew\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You give the guards permission to dock with the ship, but before they come "
"on board your crewmember slowly advances to meet them. As far as you can "
"tell no words were exchanged, but the guards offer you some supplies and say"
" the ship checks out. Best to not ask questions."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:689
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_CREW_SCAN\"]/choice[@req=\"mind\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Mind Control) Make the guards believe they have already checked your crew "
"today."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:691
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_CREW_SCAN\"]/choice[@req=\"mind\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The captain of the guard appears on the vid screen \"Back so soon friend! "
"Well, no need to waste your time further. Here, take these spare fuel "
"canisters and get on with your mission.\" Your ship is cleared to pass."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:698
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_CREW_SCAN_LIST\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Zoltan security staff board your ship and scan the crew's faces into a "
"computer. After a few tense moments of uncertainty, having not found "
"anything, they allow your ship to pass."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:701
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_CREW_SCAN_LIST\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Zoltan security staff board your ship and begin scanning the crew's "
"faces into a computer. Suddenly alarms go off and the Zoltan leap on one of "
"your crew! \"This person is wanted on five charges of Utter Villainy! "
"Surrender them to us!\""

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:703
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_CREW_SCAN_LIST\"]/event[2]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Give up your crewmember."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:705
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_CREW_SCAN_LIST\"]/event[2]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It's a tough call, but Zoltan law holds sway here. Besides, that one always "
"seemed a bit shifty."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:711
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_CREW_SCAN_LIST\"]/event[2]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"CREW_ALL\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event/removeCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Unfortunately your crewmember was taken away unharmed so your Clone Bay was "
"unable to retrieve them."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:718
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_CREW_SCAN_LIST\"]/event[2]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"CREW_ALL\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"As your ship is solely under the control of AI, you need not fear the death "
"of any crew."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:724
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_CREW_SCAN_LIST\"]/event[2]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Refuse and fight."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:726
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_CREW_SCAN_LIST\"]/event[2]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You're not going to leave anyone behind. Instead, you pull away from the "
"station with the enemy guards on board. Unfortunately, they are able to "
"sabotage your weapon system in the chaos. It's time to leave!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:742
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ZOLTAN_ROCK\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"This nebula turns out to be the hiding place of a terrified rock crew taking"
" refuge from the Zoltan border police. They don't seem prepared to risk your"
" leaving with their co-ordinates, and open fire!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:750
msgid "data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Near this beacon you find the Great Eye, transecting the cosmos. They say "
"that it gives to each what they deserve..."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:753
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Pull the ship in closer."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:757
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Leave this place."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:759
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your mission is to save the Federation, not discover new wonders around the "
"galaxy. You prepare to jump."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:765
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"As you approach, an ancient alien voice speaks to you: \"Your mission has "
"brought you great battles, and great losses. This will help ease the pain.\""
" A few minutes later someone reports medical equipment has appeared on the "
"ship!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:769
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"As you approach, an ancient alien voice speaks to you: \"Your mission has "
"brought you great battles, and great losses. This will help ease the pain.\""
" A few minutes later someone reports repair equipment has appeared on the "
"ship!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:773
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"You approach the Eye and wait, but nothing happens. All of a sudden, a "
"Zoltan ship comes out of an FTL jump near you and hail: \"You will be "
"eliminated for your illegal presence at this beacon.\" Battle Stations!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:777
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[4]/text"
msgstr ""
"You cautiously approach the Eye. The Eye, whatever it is, must sense as much"
" because the next thing you know out of nowhere a heap of scrap appears in "
"your hold!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:781
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[5]/text"
msgstr ""
"As you approach, a kaleidoscope of colors fills the viewscreen and one of "
"your crew begins to age rapidly in reverse, eventually disappearing into "
"nothingness. Let's hope they've transcended physical existence, and not just"
" been forced out of it..."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:787
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[5]/choice[@req=\"CREW_ALL\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event/removeCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"You check your Cloning Bay but it lies dormant. Whatever just happened to "
"your crewmember must be irreversible."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:794
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[5]/choice[@req=\"CREW_ALL\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"As your ship is solely under the control of AI, you need not fear the death "
"of any crew."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:799
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[6]/text"
msgstr ""
"You approach the Eye and stare into it. Out of nowhere, you see an escape "
"pod flying right at you. You give the order to catch and deliver it onto the"
" ship. Inside the pod lies a sleeping Crystal, who upon waking, is ready to "
"serve you."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:803
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[7]/text"
msgstr ""
"Approaching the Eye, you peer into it. A bright beam momentarily connects "
"your ship with the Eye, and a young Zoltan appears in the cockpit."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:807
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[8]/text"
msgstr ""
"You approach the Great Eye, and suddenly it begins to glow with a green "
"aura. Radiance starts to move your ship and forms a barrier around it. Much "
"to your surprise, you realize that it is a Zoltan Shield! You thank fate and"
" prepare for departure."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:811
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[9]/text"
msgstr ""
"You approach the Great Eye, and it begins to glow bright red. At the same "
"time the temperature starts to climb rapidly, and now your ship is ablaze! "
"You've got to get out of here!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:820
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[10]/text"
msgstr ""
"You turn the ship towards the Eye and instruct your crew to approach it. As "
"soon as you move just a few meters, it suddenly shatters into a thousand "
"pieces! A considerable portion of them get jammed in your ship's hull, "
"turning your ship into a sieve."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:853
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[11]/text"
msgstr ""
"The whole crew starts to gaze fixedly upon the Eye. Strangely, no one can "
"take their eyes off of it. The hypnotic effect lasts rather long. By the "
"time everyone comes to, you know that in that time, the Rebels must have "
"caught up by a decent amount."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:857
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[12]/text"
msgstr ""
"As soon as you get closer to the Eye, a powerful flash cuts through space "
"towards the Rebel Fleet. Telepathically, the Eye gives you the understanding"
" that your pursuers are now completely disorganized and will not catch up "
"with you anytime soon."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:861
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[13]/text"
msgstr ""
"You approach the Great Eye, but suddenly hear the sounds of a crew "
"teleporting aboard your ship! It seems that the Eye was being used as bait "
"for unsuspecting travelers like you. You prepare to fight back."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:865
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[14]/text"
msgstr ""
"You approach the Great Eye and aim all your sensors on it. Suddenly, the Eye"
" begin to vibrate — from it splits off a small splinter that starts flying "
"in your direction. You give the order to charge your weapons, but the "
"splinter changes shape and turns into a weapon! You pick it up and prepare "
"to leave."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:869
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[15]/text"
msgstr ""
"You approach the Great Eye, and it begins to glow with black light. "
"Something strange begins to happen in your engine compartment — your fuel "
"tanks strongly vibrate and heat up. Fearing an explosion, you give the order"
" to drain part of the fuel. It seems that worked, and the Eye returns back "
"to normal."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:875
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_EYE_LIST\"]/event[16]/text"
msgstr ""
"You fly up closer, and the Great Eye begins to shine with pure white light. "
"This light covers your entire ship, and you are surprised to see all your "
"hull damage disappear. You thank fate and set off towards the next beacon."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:907
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORM_ZOLTAN_SUPPLY_CHOICE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
