#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1062
#, fuzzy
msgid "data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_BOARDERS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"There are few more zealous in their customs checks than the Zoltan. A team "
"of border police beam on board. There's just a little confusion over your "
"weapons licences, but things escalate rapidly from heated discussion to "
"gunfire!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1068
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_BOARDERS_MANTIS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Mantis outcasts sometimes make the mistake of taking the Zoltan for easy"
" game. A scout moves in to attack while a boarding party beams aboard from a"
" nearby transport!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1083
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"An unarmed Zoltan transport vessel is slowly making its way toward the "
"beacon here. They hail: \"This is a Zoltan peace envoy. We carry no weapons "
"or shielding and rely on the mercy of others to communicate our message.\""

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1085
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attack them."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1089
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Hear them out."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1091
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"They continue. \"We take your silence for interested contemplation.\" They "
"talk at length about peace and harmony, but either it's beyond your simple "
"mind or it's all nonsense."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1095
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"They finish: \"Please, spread the word of enlightenment to those that have "
"not heard. Once you have, contact our brethren.\" They transmit coordinates "
"of their so-called \"brethren\"."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1102
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Leave this place."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1104
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The galaxy is at war — there's no time for talk of peace. You leave their "
"hails unanswered and charge the jump drive."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1112
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST_ATTACK\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr "You charge your weapons — this is just too easy..."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1116
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST_ATTACK\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"Just as you're preparing to attack you detect a nearby jump signature. A "
"Zoltan defense ship comes to their aid!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1122
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST2\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You arrive at the location specified by the peace-loving Zoltan, but the "
"only thing nearby is a Rebel ship, closing in fast! \"We've found you! "
"You're not getting away this time!\""

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1125
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST2\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attack."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1127
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST2\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "You power your weapons and prepare to fight."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1132
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST2\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Attempt to hail them."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1134
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST2\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"They reluctantly open communications: \"I can't imagine there's anything you"
" could say that will save you. The rebellion must destroy those that are "
"still loyal to the vanishing Federation.\""

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1136
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST2\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "\"Perhaps there could be a reconciliation of our ideals without war?\""

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1138
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST2\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Our ideals are too different to be so easily reconciled. You think this "
"could end any way but war?\""

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1140
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST2\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"The galaxy is huge — you can find a place for your ideals elsewhere without "
"causing this destruction."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1142
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST2\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"No! We will not be consigned to the backwaters of space just because we "
"don't fit into your 'Federation ideals'!\" They charge."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1147
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST2\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "\"True progress can only be achieved without bloodshed.\""

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1149
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST2\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Suddenly all indications of the Rebel ship fade away and a Zoltan fleet "
"appears around your ship. The captain of the ship you met previously "
"materializes on your bridge."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1159
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST2\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Surrender. Your ultimate destruction is inevitable. We've left scores of "
"Rebels destroyed in our wake.\""

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1161
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST2\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "They shut off communications and immediately engage."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1166
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST2\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Your Rebellion is causing millions of deaths. Your beliefs are dividing "
"the galaxy. Unity is the only option!\""

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1168
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST2\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"The people of the weak Federation believe they are 'equal' to aliens. The "
"sacrifice of BILLIONS of alien or human lives are justified if it means we "
"reach our full potential!\" They charge."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1178
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_PEACE_QUEST_REWARD\"]/loadEventList/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Although your methods are crude and most certainly ineffective, it is "
