msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTON\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"This sector belongs to the Zoltons — a once peaceful race whose political "
"views differ from their fellow Zoltans. Now they've been involuntarily "
"dragged into the war between the Federation and the Rebellion."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1342
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTON\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"Zoltons are famous for their ability to create the most solid shield systems"
" on their ships. If you don't violate their order, then perhaps they will "
"help modernize your shields."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1343
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTON\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"This sector was captured by a group of Zoltan separatists. After the coup "
"they called themselves Zoltons and introduced a special order in the "
"territories under their jurisdiction."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1344
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTON\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"Zoltons — the best in the Galaxy when it comes to specializing in ion and "
"beam weaponry. It's extremely dangerous to fight them without additional "
"shield layers."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1345
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTON\"]/text[5]"
msgstr ""
"Nebula beacons play a key role in the navigation of this sector, so the "
"Zoltons leave their drones there to protect against intruders."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1354
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"STORE_ZOLTON\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"Near the beacon, an enterprising Zolton has put together a small store-"
"station. After making sure you can be trusted, they give your ship access."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1355
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"STORE_ZOLTON\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"The nearby station offers a list of goods banned in this sector. Why the "
"local Zoltons have not yet closed it down is a good question..."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1356
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"STORE_ZOLTON\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"A trade platform nearby is broadcasting about its discounts and new "
"products. You fly closer with curiousity. The Zolton store owner assures you"
" that all equipment is absolutely legal."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1368
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ZOLTON\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"Away from the beacon, you notice a small cluster of Zolton ships. But before"
" you even get the chance to stabilise all the ship's systems, they're gone "
"without a trace."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1369
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ZOLTON\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"You exit the FTL jump near the beacon. With surprise, you notice that the "
