"extremes in their technical solutions..."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1370
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ZOLTON\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"You have to admit — Zolton territory is in fact quite a beautiful place. You"
" admire the views outside the window while the FTL drive charges."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1371
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ZOLTON\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"A Zolton ship is waiting for something at this beacon, but before you can "
"greet them, they've left."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1372
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ZOLTON\"]/text[5]"
msgstr ""
"It's quite beautiful next to the beacon, but you don't have the opportunity "
"to admire the local species — the Federation is in danger!"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1373
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING_ZOLTON\"]/text[6]"
msgstr ""
"Several lasers flash by as they cut through the space near your ship. You "
"notice how a group of Zoltons and pirates are making FTL jumps away from "
"this beacon. It looks like you're a bit late for an armed local clash."

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1382
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"ZOLTON_FIGHT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
